@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = <REPLACE_WITH_CLIENT_JWT>
@orderId = 1
@restaurantId = 1

### Add review for RESTAURANT (CLIENT, only after DELIVERED)
POST {{host}}/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "orderId": {{orderId}},
  "targetType": "RESTAURANT",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Pyszne jedzenie i szybka dostawa."
}

### Add review for COURIER (CLIENT, only after DELIVERED and courier assigned)
POST {{host}}/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "orderId": {{orderId}},
  "targetType": "COURIER",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Mi≈Çy kurier, dostawa na czas."
}

### Public list reviews for restaurant
GET {{host}}/api/restaurants/{{restaurantId}}/reviews



